data.description: This stunning 3 bedroom 2 bath house combines elegance, comfort and breathtaking STRIP VIEWS in the much desired Bellano community. This home is nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac, just a short walk from the Lake Las Vegas Sports Club, driving range, golf course and numerous walking paths. You can relax out front and take in the mountain views in the gated courtyard. The backyard is an entertainer’s delight on an elevated lot with a custom outdoor kitchen including a grill, mini fridge and smoker. Inside you will be greeted by lots of natural light, an open layout and luxurious features and finishes throughout including wood shutters in the bedrooms. The owner's suite offers a large walk-in shower and spacious closet. The unique large laundry room doubles as a utility space or mudroom. The garage features an epoxy flooring, built-in garage cabinets and storage racks. Don't miss this rare opportunity for luxurious Lake Las Vegas living!
